1. Definitions
“Software” means the source code, build scripts, and documentation in this repository.
“Official Build Artifacts” means prebuilt ISOs, packages, update repositories, container images, and signing keys released by Nithron.
“Non-Commercial Use” means use by an individual for personal, educational, research, or open-source contribution purposes, with no direct or indirect monetary compensation or consideration and not on behalf of any for-profit entity.
“Commercial Use” means any use that is not Non-Commercial Use, including use by or on behalf of a for-profit entity, providing services to third parties, hosting, resale, paid support, consulting, or any monetized distribution.
“Trademarks” means the names “Nithron”, “NithronOS”, “nOS”, related logos, wordmarks, and brand assets.

